WOW.  I can do that!  Thanks Mike.  Now - for clueless newbies like myself -
can you do a video of you recording using this device so we can see how that
is done.  I think you and the others should write the next ITC for dummies! 



You&#39;re great!

k



  _____  

From: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com [mailto:EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of
Misty Dawn
Sent: Monday, November 26, 2007 2:08 PM
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: RE: [EVP-ITC] Re: Mini AM/FM Hack Site



Yeah that was awesome video Mike...that I think I can do or anyone else can
do just as you showed. I heard them say your name did you? I also heard
someone elses name.



I also got a chance to catch up on Franks videos hehehe again I&#39;m hearing
some results in there responding to your chatter. Gotta love the live
feedback! I have been getting that alot lately using different methods.



Misty





Frank Sumption &lt;franks-boxes@...&gt; wrote:

Even better! I thought those were FM only. 

 Frank




